    * Optimized MACROTEXT

    /* xHarbour now support complex macros referencing declared symbols, where Clipper produces an error:

          LOCAL cMacro  := "mVar"

          PRIVATE mVar1 := "I'm mVar"

          ? &cMacro.1

       Complex macros will now work faster, due to compile time optimization.

     */

