    + Added logic to detect Alt-C in hb_vmExecute() every 65535 pCodes.

  /* Now xHarbour support Alt-C in long loops, like Clipper does */

  /* Now xHarbour Function/Procedure/Properties/Methods are 5 times faster,
     and are even faster than Clipper!!!

    Here are the latest results for 1,000,000 iterrations:

              Proc    Func
              -----   -----
    xHarbour:  1.97    2.66
    Clipper :  2.58    3.41
    Harbour : 11.92   14.31
  */

