2002-01-06 14:00:00 UTC+0700 Andi Jahja <andijahja@cbn.net.id>
   * source/compiler/harbour.c
     + BOOL hb_comp_bNoStartUp = FALSE, initialization for option to create
       C-source with startup flag ( HB_FS_FIRST ).
   * source/compiler/cmdcheck.c
     + additional arguments to switch /n :
       /n or /n0 = do not generate implicit procedure but generate
        startup flag ( HB_FS_FIRST )
       /n1 = do not generate implicit procedure and startup flag ( HB_FS_FIRST )
       /n- = forces implicit procedure generation
   * source/compiler/genc.c
     + switch /n1 creates C-Source with no HB_FS_FIRST ( no startup )
   * source/compiler/hbusage.c
     ! bump copyright year to 2002
     + add info on switch /n1
   * include/hbdefs.h
     + add argument __EXPORT__ for exporting functions so that exports
       will be done only on explicit request by #define __EXPORT__ in makefile
       or make switch ( -D__EXPORT__ )
     ! typo : _declspec => __declspec
   * include/hbcomp.h
     + BOOL hb_comp_bNoStartUp, public variable for generating C-source with
       no_startup flag ( HB_FS_FIRST ) option.
   + hrbdll.bc
     makefile for harbour.dll with Borland CPP 5.5.1
   + dll_55.bat
     batch file to create harbour.dll with Borland CPP 5.5.1
   * tests/dll55.bat
     batch file to create application with harbour.dll ( BCC 5.5.1 )
   * tests/dll.mak
     makefile to create application with harbour.dll ( BCC 5.5.1 )

