  * xharbour/source/rtl/type.c
  * xharbour/source/rtl/valtostr.c
  * xharbour/source/rtl/version.c
    * First installment of an overhaul optimization of the RT.
      so far only taking advantage of hb_retc[]Adopt() from fastitem.c.

      After thoutough testings system appears stable and already faster
      than Harbour.

